{"tid":1460184,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[英中日韓] 去機場嘅入嚟 遊客一定會睇嘅接機文宣","createTime":"2019-08-13T01:42:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T13:35:21.000Z","uid":28759,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"dc899b02628869433c1bb9c34d96c17b6f7eb20e","tid":1460184,"uid":28759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T01:42:46.000Z","msg":"黑警有幾仆街一張紙寫唔晒<br />\n所以加咗句叫佢地上網搵嘢嚟<br />\n英文︰Reddit r/HongKong<br />\n日文︰周庭 twitter<br />\n韓文︰<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hkantielabinkorean/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhkantielabinkorean%2F&d=IX2zbuQlYI18gOdM245y97tp0LkHB2EL0pKzUaHUqTQ%3D&h=0a9a6e39\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hkantielabinkorean/</a><br />\n希望佢地可以有興趣睇多啲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YtgkeOm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYtgkeOm.png&h=8907bc7a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/o6N3W1K.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo6N3W1K.png&h=2b596b03&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vV0w5U5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvV0w5U5.png&h=2be3cdb1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dbr4Gts.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fdbr4Gts.png&h=70c9ec67&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qYOKGtv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqYOKGtv.png&h=ddd47351&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Q2NWxAc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ2NWxAc.png&h=0fc61770&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oGJramO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoGJramO.png&h=2d3a7db5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pxMHs8w.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpxMHs8w.png&h=cefe2a06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YuOVN8z.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYuOVN8z.png&h=fc53a0eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dEuaB1X.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdEuaB1X.png&h=1585ca2f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nPDF 內附 英、中、日、韓<br />\n得英文有黑白版（因為懶）<br />\n千祈唔好拎紅黑版去印黑白<br />\n呢個稿係想用嚟印彩色接機舉牌<br />\n有人問你就可以逐格解釋下發生咩事<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.mediafire.com/file/nebr71rqunmgxk4/812ariport_all.pdf/file\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mediafire.com%2Ffile%2Fnebr71rqunmgxk4%2F812ariport_all.pdf%2Ffile&d=IX2zbuQlYI18gOdM245y97tp0LkHB2EL0pKzUaHUqTQ%3D&h=c0ba7b68\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.mediafire.com/file/nebr71rqunmgxk4/812ariport_all.pdf/file</a>"},{"pid":"4d7a5c0a70777b56fd6dfc5e7e7dc7f0b74f4396","tid":1460184,"uid":28759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T01:47:23.000Z","msg":"推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cd91d52c4f9b00fbb1c8941dc6ab87882c12bdb","tid":1460184,"uid":120377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T01:49:09.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"349e429e0c712afd896bf6c71ec997dee20302f4","tid":1460184,"uid":28759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T01:49:20.000Z","msg":"印印印印啊"},{"pid":"774096c88a9ef81c6023cc891049fc01f9994818","tid":1460184,"uid":260036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T01:50:10.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"f993063f200b179868a89d791faa8afb6852af5f","tid":1460184,"uid":141947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T01:50:33.